## Idea

The _Gelfand-Naimark theorem_ says that every [[C*-algebra]] is [[isomorphism|isomorphic]] to a $C^\ast$-algebra of [[bounded linear operators]] on a [[Hilbert space]].

## Related concepts

* [[Gelfand spectrum]]

* [[Gelfand duality]]


